HEADWORD: Holostraca
<hw>Ho*los"tra*ca</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
fr. Gr. <grk>"o`los</grk> whole + <?/ shell of a testacean.]</ety>
